  "description": {
   "en": "[Look closely, listen up, and learn well – about how to kill a person]   \n  \nAfter school, I have private tutoring classes with my \"kind\" teacher. Because of that, my classmates suspect that my teacher and I are in a forbidden relationship. While there may be some truth to it, it’s a far cry from the “lovey-dovey relationship” that one might expect. My teacher is a serial killer, and I'm his disciple in the art of murder.  \n  \n\"Sensei, I learned a lot today.\"   \n  \nOnce again, a bell quietly echoes at the crime scene, heralding the end of today's supplementary lesson.  \n  \nThis is the story of a twisted romance between a teacher with a penchant for killing and a student hell-bent on revenge.  \n  \n[ALT SYNOPSIS]  \nAlice's parents were killed when she was young. She saw the killer and made the promise to herself to kill him. Little did she know that when she would go to high school, the killer would become her teacher.",
   "pt-br": "Quando criança os pais de Arisu foram mortos. Felizmente, pode ver o assassino e fez uma promessa a si mesma de matá-lo no futuro, mas mal sabia ela que o culpado se tornaria seu professor do ensino médio…"
  },
